{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "喪禮", "storyInfo": "安多恩一直照料的木攀獸母親去世，但他的悲傷很快就被抹去，他意識到牧首承諾給他的未來是多麼恐怖。費德里科與離群的薩科塔們展開對峙，並最終允許他們作為助力入城。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g8_laterano_dwelling", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "aw"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "aw"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞機……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "得改口了哦。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經被禁足，原則上教皇廳應該不允許任何人前來探視才對啊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報備過了。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛接任，在事務交接上難免有一些倉促，來請教前任樞機，再正常不過。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你適應得很快嘛，阿摩斯樞機。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得你之前還說，自己是個沒什麼追求的人。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞……小姐，我不是來趁機炫耀什麼的，我們之間本來也不是什麼勾心鬥角的上下級關係吧。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果你是來問蕾繆樂的行蹤，我已經在前幾輪詢問中說過很多次——確實無可奉告。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我想問您另外一個問題。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安小姐，您願意犧牲自己的事業，只是為了保護妹妹，還是，您真的相信她說的……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從降生儀式，到萬國峰會……拉特蘭最近發生的所有事都很不對勁。我們像是，患上了某種疾病。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，這個問題沒有什麼不同。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我想請您看一樣東西。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿摩斯點開了自己的終端，遞給蕾繆安。"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬國信使的申請函。我希望能夠成為萬國信使，負責玻利瓦爾一帶的政府溝通任務。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想離開拉特蘭？為什麼？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和我的妻子……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年我們大吵了一架，不歡而散。等我再回到家，她已經出去執行任務了，前往卡茲戴爾附近的荒野，處理薩卡茲侵擾商隊的事情。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一直是這樣的脾氣，聽不進別人的話。那時候是冬天，我心想，她應該春天才能回來，我還來得及做點什麼……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來的事情，我也告訴過您，墮天啊驅逐啊什麼的。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第七廳專司情報、國安和外交，工作上有一些便利，我花了很長的時間，終於打聽到了她的下落。於是我就想著……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能理解。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，你剛剛說的怪事是指？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道萬國信使的選拔標準有多嚴格，憑我的能力，實在是……所以這份申請，一直躺在我的信箱裡。直到……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你接任第七廳樞機後，批准了自己的那份申請？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通知我接任樞機一職的時候，帕特里奇昂閣下說我從來都只是缺乏一個契機……", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然他肯定另有所指，但我這個沒出息的頭腦，第一時間想到的就是這件事。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我點過批准之後，這份申請就……消失了。沒有收到任何申請被駁回的消息，沒有任何記錄可查。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它就那麼消失在我的終端裡，像是、像是從來沒有存在過。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#10$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照流程，那份申請不論我批准與否都不會被通過，我不可能被允許立刻辭去樞機職務，成為萬國信使。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況所有萬國信使都已經被召回拉特蘭，哪怕真的當上了，我也沒機會去見奧羅拉。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "批准那份申請對我來說，連彌補都不算，那就只是一絲微不足道的慰藉。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰會想著把這微不足道的慰藉也抹消掉呢？", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，這足以成為一條線索……讓我懷疑這個拉特蘭是否真實。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#7$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許……您妹妹想做的事情，是正確的。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿摩斯樞機，你有向其他人提起這件事嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒、沒有。一整個晚上我都沒辦法閉眼休息……想來想去，也只有您可以分享了。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#4$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿摩斯樞機，我在想，這是否是什麼新的審訊手段。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以相信我，蕾繆安小姐。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都有自己真正在意的東西……也都不多。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#8$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很有趣的發言，阿摩斯先生。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對了，今天，育嬰聖堂會舉行一場更盛大的降生儀式。", "name": "阿摩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1783_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 100.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.15, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.15, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“每個人終其一生，都在為死亡這件事做準備。”"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕在潮石鎮那樣被飢荒和瘟疫沖刷得一無所有的地方，也會有年邁的老人在閉眼前一刻，舔舔乾裂的嘴唇，悠悠說出類似的話。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一句老生常談，只不過對有些人來說是飲恨的總結，而對另一些人來說是不懷遺憾的感喟。但它們的前提是一樣的——"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡，是生命的終點。"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（疑惑地拱頭）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（緊張地搧翅）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，孩子，你的母親已經不會再回應我們了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……牠已經死去。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_birdlingchirp_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低聲地嚶鳴）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母獸已經沒有了鼻息，安多恩緩緩闔上牠的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幼獸靠了過來，牠顫抖著，連毛色都變得暗淡。安多恩將牠抱上自己的膝頭，對上牠的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幼獸的聲音含混不清，安多恩也不懂獸的語言，但他清晰地感受到悲傷。悲傷像是平靜河面下奔湧的水流——幼獸的，自己的。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡總是伴隨著新生，你的母親只是在自知生命無可挽回後，選擇將生的希望留給你。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠用盡了所有力氣，最終做到了這件事情。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的第一課。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_birdlingchirp_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低聲地嚶鳴）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潮石鎮、那個有鐘樓的小鎮、荒野上的修道院以及此刻……我經歷過許多類似的時刻，如今我再次經歷，體悟更加深刻。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬物都會在它既定的旅程中走向終結，所以意義的延續才顯得難能可貴。"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡，是一場告別。"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是死者對生者的贈禮，是生者拯救自己的起點。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，別恐懼。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該悲哀，你應該銘記……我與你一起。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩前輩，牠的葬禮由您主持，我就不進去了。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首呢？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首恐怕暫時無法過來，她在準備接下來的降生儀式，為聖堂內的所有非薩科塔賦予光環……她讓我跟您說聲抱歉。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……無妨。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們習慣了隆重地迎接新生，而葬禮總是簡單的。告訴牧首，我會稍微晚一點返回崗位。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還好嗎？", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母親的離世太過突然，這孩子還太小，很難抵禦那樣強烈的悲傷，我需要陪在牠身邊。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，安多恩前輩，牧首擔心的是您。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首說，您和她一起陪伴了這位母親良久，您內心的苦痛不言而喻。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是一個善思的人，每一段旅程都會給您啟發，但在那之前，也會讓您困頓。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於這個孩子……牠是奇蹟，牠有能力走出陰霾。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首讓我轉告您，未來，拉特蘭每一個新生的生命，都不會被外在的災厄和內在的悲傷所擊倒。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們生而平等，也將勇敢而強大……拉特蘭會幫助他們做到。", "name": "保育員"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 3.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩感覺到木攀獸幼獸在輕拱自己的手臂。他想撫摸小獸，但小獸奮力地張開翅膀，推開了他的手。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_comfortbell", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小獸盤旋著飛起，落在房間中央的安撫鈴上，與安撫鈴一同發出悅耳的聲響。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩不解地望向幼獸，哪怕頭頂光環行走了幾十年，在剎那間看見小獸無比明亮的光環後依然感覺刺眼。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（用力地搧翅）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_birdlingchirp_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（高聲地嚶鳴）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他與小獸朝夕相處，這些動作代表著什麼，他十分清楚。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是小獸在邀他一起玩耍。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從來不會拒絕孩子們的保育員呆立原地。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想藉助共感傳達自己的悲傷，想以最委婉的方式拒絕這難以理解的邀請。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最終，他只是走上前去，牽住木攀獸的爪，與小獸一同、與安撫鈴一同，在空曠的房間正中跳起了圓舞的步伐。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "木攀獸興奮地鳴叫著，尖銳的啼鳴久久不能散去；牠的羽毛在燈光下熠熠生輝，在旋轉中展露出全部的光澤。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的步伐越來越快，安多恩只能勉強撇過頭去，望向母獸的遺體，試圖確認自己的情緒。他猛地意識到——"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己早已不再悲傷。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他與那小獸一樣快樂，他與那小獸一樣美麗，他與那小獸一樣，滿懷希望地向未來獻上高歌與舞蹈。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們飛旋的步伐在地面上、在空氣中劃出一個又一個美麗的圓環。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……這就是……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#9$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#9$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有免於苦痛的本能……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#9$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻沒有悲傷與哀悼的資格？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#9$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道這就是薩科塔，這就是生命的奇蹟？！", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#5$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人回答他歇斯底里的詰問。他的牧首正在啟聖大廳，為人們賦予一頂又一頂美麗的光環。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯獨他自己，突兀地停下了腳步，不自覺地想起了一場葬禮，一場本來不應該存在於他記憶中的葬禮。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 1.5, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鳶尾花田，小小的孩子，一些殘忍卻真誠的傾訴與禱告，鐘聲。"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "31_g4_mini12_village", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "crwd1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "crwd1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還、還是沒有回應嗎？", "name": "墮天使A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1805_1#2$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，奧羅拉？", "name": "墮天使A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1805_1#2$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不信就過來自己聽。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_recorderglitch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耳朵要聾了……裡面各種雜音，什麼也聽不到啊！", "name": "墮天使A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1806_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉，這到底是怎麼回事？", "name": "墮天使B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1806_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在質問我？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1806_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟你是銃騎，起碼曾經是，你自然比我們更懂這些東西。", "name": "墮天使B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1806_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也說了，“曾經”。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些雜音夠吵了，如果你們再繼續吵，我有很多辦法讓你們閉嘴。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1806_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "墮天使們"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "修女……", "name": "玻利瓦爾小孩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別害怕，雨果。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1", "posfrom": "70,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（奧羅拉，孩子們正在看，別這樣。）", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這些薩科塔都是突遭變故，從其他國家不遠萬里趕回來的。他們頭上還頂著破碎的光環，滿心恐慌卻得不到安撫……）", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭的城際網路系統向來很穩定，城外各個聚落的通訊裝置會由專人定期維護。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一根緊急通訊樁離拉特蘭城只有三公里，按理說是最不該出問題的。但我已經透過特殊頻道呼叫了十幾次了，都沒有回應。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，難道拉特蘭真的完蛋了？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉，辛苦你再試幾次吧。", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#3$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "努艾達，你看起來比他們還要緊張。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#16$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "努艾達沒有回答。幾個孩子跑了過來，抓住她的裙襬，隨著她的目光一起看向前方。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這個小鎮，已經能窺見拉特蘭城的外圍，潔白的城牆與流雲同色，像是誤入凡塵的聖靈居所，本不該存世的奇蹟。"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而遠行者此刻與它相隔咫尺，他們風塵僕僕，疲憊不堪，已經破碎的光環和光翼在荒野裡顯得更加黯淡。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朝聖者終抵終途，然而苦旅真的能就此結束嗎？"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就是，拉特蘭……", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#6$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，看樣子城裡的人是火燒眉毛，連自己都顧不過來了。收拾東西，我們直接進城。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，總不能就這樣在這裡等著。不管了，走！", "name": "墮天使A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1806_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，沒有得到教皇廳的允許，擅自進城的話……", "name": "墮天使B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1806_1#2$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這些墮天的罪人決定回拉特蘭，難道得到教皇廳的允許了？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我你回來是想幫拉特蘭報恩，那樣的話我可以先把你解決了。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "crwd1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停下腳步，到此為止。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_sys_act16side_intro", "key": "$m_sys_act16side_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不得進入拉特蘭。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，竟然是一位公證所的執行者。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是奧羅拉？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認識我？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到你的通訊後，我在公證所查閱了你的資料。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧羅拉，前公民編號LC0073458，前銃騎第三小隊隊長，於1090年冬率隊前往北部荒野護送拉特蘭商隊，並與薩卡茲傭兵爆發衝突。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你成功完成了任務。但在回程途中，移動修道院遭遇了小型天災，被押解的薩卡茲傭兵趁機暴動，被你當場格殺。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，當同行的銃騎試圖如實記述任務報告時，為了掩蓋因自己的過激手段招致的罪責，你竟然舉銃威脅對方。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混亂中你殺害了同僚，也因此被剝奪公民身分、永久驅逐出拉特蘭。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，執行者先生，你面無表情地說完這一大堆，就是想告訴我，拉特蘭從來沒有忘記我的罪？", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看你面前的這幾百人。他們有一些是像我一樣遭到驅逐的墮天使，有一些是基於種種原因脫離聖城的離群者……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至還有一群人，從來沒有見過聖城，他們在玻利瓦爾那樣的爛地方，信奉著拉特蘭的教義……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒看見這些人的光環嗎？這是墮天還是病？他們跋山涉水來到這裡，求一個解，求個說法，求個心安。", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而拉特蘭，卻只是派出一個執行者將我們擋在城外？！", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunequip", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunload", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$shotgunreload", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_revolverchange", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunequip", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunequip", "channel": "2", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "61_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越來越多的離群薩科塔圍了上來，他們將費德里科包圍在中心，朝著他舉起手中的武器。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是離開拉特蘭久了一點，只是忘了怎麼和其他薩科塔一樣生活……現在就要被拒之門外？", "name": "離群的薩科塔A"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "律法責罰罪孽，但你告訴我，我老老實實在萊塔尼亞過了二十年，我犯了什麼罪？", "name": "離群的薩科塔B"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果律法如此殘酷，應該受罰的就不是我們，而是你——你和你的同伴，律法的牙獸！", "name": "墮天使A"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者，我當初墮天就是因為你們懲罰不了該懲罰的人！現在看來，你們的本事始終用錯了方向！", "name": "墮天使B"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科沉默地看著眼前的人群。"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "路燈不合時宜地亮著，為人們的臉平添一抹怪異的色彩。恐慌、焦躁、憤怒、疑惑、驚懼……種種表情讓他們的五官變得扭曲。"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們握住武器的手在顫抖，騷亂一觸即發。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但費德里科有能力控制眼下的局面。憑自己的反應速度，他有把握儘快解決對方的帶頭者，直接鎮壓剩下的人。"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一直以來，他都是這麼做的，而且效果顯著。"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費德里科是一位優秀的公證所執行者，這是他成為執行者的第八年，對這項工作早已得心應手。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時，這也是他被加上聖徒名號的第三個年頭，除了一朵已經被焚毀的花、幾個偶然相識的人，沒有誰能給他啟發或指點。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看著眼前緊張的人群，緩緩將手從腰間移開，示意自己的手與守護銃保持了足夠的距離。"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來這裡，並不是為了重申拉特蘭曾對各位下達的判決。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來這裡，並不代表公證所、教皇廳及拉特蘭的任何官方立場。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位不得進入拉特蘭城，是因為城中發生了一些遠超常識的異變，你們的到來，或許會讓局勢更加混亂。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要一點時間，我會儘量向你們解釋清楚。", "name": "費德里科"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1782_1#12$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4187_graceb_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "努艾達"}, "figure_art": "avg_4187_graceb_1#16$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1805_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1806_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "墮天使們"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cellodoubth", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅？你不應該離開聖城。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，我已經見到了博士……我來找你，自然也是博士的意思。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士的發現證實了你我的猜想。拉特蘭全城陷入了某種群體性的幻夢，但此刻，夢境中的異變正在與現實疊加……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災異正在吞噬整座城市。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……類似於巫王的帕維永崩解後，荒域對崔林特爾梅的侵襲？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概吧，我也並不能完全理解。但毫無疑問的是，幾百萬拉特蘭人正深陷在虛幻與現實的拉扯中，我們需要新的助力。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這些背律者和離群者。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恰巧出現的不和諧音，往往能成為演奏中有趣的變奏。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同意博士的判斷。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果災異覆蓋的範圍是整座拉特蘭城，他們極有可能會在入城的同時進入幻夢。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才來找你，順便帶來了我的琴。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}